OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FOne in seven train services will be
OL,7,Faxed on Avanti West Coast's busiest
OL,8,Froutes following a Government request
OL,9,Fto reduce spending, the operator said.
OL,11,FAbout 38 daily weekday services will
OL,12,Fbe removed from timetables for six
OL,13,Fweeks from 20 July.
OL,15,FThe company usually runs 248 daily
OL,16,Fservices on the affected routes, which
OL,17,Fconnect London Euston with Birmingham,
OL,18,FLiverpool, and Manchester via the West
OL,19,FCoast Main Line.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
