PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast said it proposed
OL,7,Fremoving some services with lower
OL,8,Fdemand in response to a request from
OL,9,Fthe Department for Transport (DfT) to
OL,10,Fcut costs.
OL,12,FThe plan was approved by officials at
OL,13,Fthe department.
OL,15,FAvanti West Coast ` a joint venture
OL,16,Fbetween FirstGroup (70%) and Italian
OL,17,Fstate operator Trenitalia (30%) ` said
OL,18,Fthe measure will cause minimum
OL,19,Fdisruption to passengers and will not
OL,20,Freduce revenue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FAll train services operated under DfT
OL,7,Fcontracts are being transferred to
OL,8,Fpublic ownership.
OL,10,FEven companies such as Avanti West
OL,11,FCoast, which are yet to lose their
OL,12,Fservices, have their finances heavily
OL,13,Finfluenced by the DfT.
OL,15,FThis is because of contracts
OL,16,Fintroduced in March 2020 at the start
OL,17,Fof the coronavirus pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
