PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FAn Avanti West Coast spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "From 20 July to 28 August, we
OL,8,Fwill be operating an amended timetable
OL,9,Fbetween London and Birmingham,
OL,10,FLiverpool and Manchester on weekdays.
OL,12,F"To ensure minimal impact to those
OL,13,Ftravelling between the affected dates,
OL,14,Fthese changes will only affect routes
OL,15,Fon which we operate more than one
OL,16,Ftrain per hour, during typically less
OL,17,Fbusy periods of the day ` maximising
OL,18,Falternative journey options.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
