OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,F"We'd like to encourage customers
OL,7,Fplanning to make journeys during this
OL,8,Ftime to plan ahead, and thank them for
OL,9,Ftheir understanding."
OL,11,FAffected services are being removed
OL,12,Ffrom online ticketing services before
OL,13,Fbecoming available for purchase.
OL,15,FThe Department for Transport has been
OL,16,Fapproached for comment via the Press
OL,17,FAssociation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
