PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast temporarily slashed
OL,7,Fits timetables in August 2022 in an
OL,8,Fattempt to reduce short-notice
OL,9,Fcancellations after a sharp decline in
OL,10,Fthe number of drivers voluntarily
OL,11,Fworking on rest days for extra pay,
OL,12,Famid industrial relations disputes
OL,13,Facross Britain's railways.
OL,15,FIt has since boosted its capacity
OL,16,Fbeyond pre-coronavirus levels.
OL,18,FThe operator said the latest reduction
OL,19,Fin services is not because of a lack
OL,20,Fof resources.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
