PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779181630
OL,3,CTrain operator to axe services after
OL,4,CGovernment asks it to save money
OL,6,FOffice of Rail and Road figures show
OL,7,FGovernment funding of the rail
OL,8,Findustry's operations was #11.9
OL,9,Fbillion in the year to the end of
OL,10,FMarch 2025.
OL,12,FThat was down 7% from #12.7 billion
OL,13,Fduring the previous 12 months, but
OL,14,Fremained 47% above the total of #8.1
OL,15,Fbillion in 2019/20.
OL,17,FLast year's #11.9 billion figure
OL,18,Frepresented 46% of the industry's
OL,19,Fcosts, with fares revenue funding the
OL,20,Fvast majority of the rest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
